reviews.title: LG Motion
reviews.comment: This app needs news of amber alerts, crimes, weather and widget make it like a morning news paper.
reviews.author: Gilberto Marcos Banuelos Garcia

reviews.title: Intrusive ads and too much fluff content.
reviews.comment: Decent app but the ads are very intrusive - just pops up a black screen.  There is also a lot of fluff content. It primarily is two things: chat questions made to look like actual stories and stories that are designed only to generate clicks.
reviews.author: Chris Yarnell

reviews.title: Socially Inept
reviews.comment: I like the DMN but do not like this app. There are some great stories and articles I want my friends and family to read but there are Zip, Nada, No options for sharing via email, FB, Twitter, etc. This is an easy fix and would certainly bring more readers to DMN.
reviews.author: Lon Bason

reviews.title: They don\'t seem to want subscribers
reviews.comment: I have paid for the android e-edition twice now. After everything worked just fine for one day, can\'t access subscriber content the next day. Frustrating.
reviews.author: Trey Hill

reviews.title: Money grab
reviews.comment: A large portion of the articles require a subscription. The Guardian and Washington Post don\'t require subscriptions and offer better apps.  If you want the same news (only not focused on Dallas), get the Star Telegram\'s app. They also don\'t require a subscription.
reviews.author: Christopher Atwood

reviews.title: Above Average
reviews.comment: I like it and have no problems with ads and i\'m a daily subscriber to the DMN. Whats the problem with ads folks?  All newspapers have ads in them. Get over it you complainers !
reviews.author: Rick Richards

reviews.title: Ads with subscription
reviews.comment: Why are there ads on the bottom of every article and some half or even full page ads when I pay a monthly fee to use the app. Uninstalling and canceling my subscription unless this is fixed.
reviews.author: A Google User

reviews.title: Useless
reviews.comment: Lots of ads and subscribe nonsense.  Uninstall.
reviews.author: susan maier

reviews.title: Quality paper
reviews.comment: The definitive source of Dallas news. Reasonable price.
reviews.author: Ben Guthrie

reviews.title: Weak app
reviews.comment: Needs too many things to list.
reviews.author: JP Johnson

reviews.comment: No use unless you pay. I suggest getting local med from other FREE apps.
reviews.author: Eric L

reviews.title: Not free
reviews.comment: Don\'t bother not free waste time sing in all the time bs
reviews.author: A Google User

reviews.title: How about the full edition for subscribers?
reviews.comment: I know you can do it,  I can get it on my PC. I will change my rating to 5 stars if that ever happens.
reviews.author: George Lass

reviews.title: No E-Edition
reviews.comment: I have been waiting for months for the DMN Android app and it is here but has no value to me. I thought it support the E-Edition by Olive Software. It does not. You have to access the E-Edition with your browser - very cumbersome.
reviews.author: A Google User

reviews.title: Not impressed
reviews.comment: Price increases and paying monthly for content, come on DMN! Just called and cancelled paper delivery and all online content.
reviews.author: A Google User

reviews.comment: Tried to download twice and use. Failed both times on my galaxy with forced closes.
reviews.author: A Google User

reviews.title: Finally an Android version. Need a tablet version
reviews.comment: It\'s nice to be able to take advantage of subscriber services on my android device. It would be very nice, however, if DMN would offer a version that is optimized for Honeycomb similar to the iPad app.
reviews.author: A Google User

reviews.comment: Have installed twice and it consistently force closes.  Uninstalling for good.
reviews.author: A Google User

reviews.title: Time waste
reviews.comment: Can\'t read all articles without subscribing. Very limited in readable content.
reviews.author: A Google User

reviews.title: Not 4 motorola atrix
reviews.comment: Will only let me read the local sports. Local news, politics, ect. will not load articles.
reviews.author: A Google User
